      "notes": "**Duplicating clips** can be useful for creating variations and iterations of designs, A/B testing, or overlaying haptic data from one clip onto another. \n\nTo duplicate a clip, right click the selected clip and choose **‘Duplicate’** in the dropdown menu. This will create an exact copy of the selected clip.\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/duplicate.png\"/>\n\n\nThe duplicate clip will appear below, marked with (1). You can rename the clip by double-clicking on its name.\n\n\n\n",
