      "markers": [],
      "notes": "The Tool Bar includes everything you need to edit envelopes and modify content within the editor window.\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/toolbar.png\"/></p>\n\n<b>Selection tool:</b> Select and move elements in the editor.\n\n<b>Pen tool:</b> Create freeform haptics, add points or extend your envelope.\n\n<b>Marker tool:</b> Set markers within the clip for reference.\n\n<b>Emphasis tool:</b> Add emphasis points to your envelope.\n\n<b>Trim tool:</b> Adjust the duration of your clips.\n/newpage\nYou can switch between tools either by clicking the Tool Bar icons or using keyboard shortcuts.\n\n<p align=\"center\"> <img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/shortcuts.png\"/>\n",
