      "lastUpdate": 1750428386735,
      "notes": "Clip Types\nThere are five different clip types, each with its own icon for easy identification: Mono Audio Clip, Stereo Audio Clip, Stereo Left Channel, Stereo Right Channel, freeform Haptics.\n\n<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://./assets/fileicons.png\" />\n\n/newpage\nYou can add a new audio or freeform clip to your project by clicking the plus (+) icon.\n\n<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://./assets/addnewclip.png\" />\n\nYou can change the name of the project by double clicking the project name.\n\nYou can right-click on a clip to: group or ungroup, duplicate, split stereo channels or delete/remove the clip.\n\n<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://./assets/rightclick.png\" />\n"
    },
    {
      "clipId": "1070a3d1-863a-4cbb-bc47-ca63e4f8f46b",
      "name": "Pen tool",
