      "lastUpdate": 1750428635993,
      "notes": "<p align=\"center\"> <img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/pentool.png\"/>\n\nThe Pen tool allows for quick prototyping by letting you draw haptic effects without the need for an audio track. \n\nTo dive deeper into this workflow, refer to the **Freeform Haptics** tutorial."
    },
    {
      "clipId": "0ae2ce39-7026-4d05-8703-188149efef9b",
