      "lastUpdate": 1750428970090,
      "notes": "Select the clips you want to export in the Clip Navigator, then click the Export button in the lower right corner.\n<p align=\"center\"> <img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/export.png\" /> </p>\nYou can choose from three export formats:\n\n**.haptic**\nA hardware-agnostic file format used with the Meta Haptics SDK\n\n**.ahap**\nFor integration with iOS devices\n\n**.wav** \nFor platforms that support waveform-based haptics"
    }
  ],
